            . Last Sunday night I lost a cloath coat, and two waistcoats, from on board a ship lying off <placeName id="t17530607-7-crimeloc29">New Crane, in the parish of Shadwell</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17530607-7-crimeloc29" type="placeName" value="New Crane, in the parish of Shadwell"></interp>
